title: Doris_M1_Start
tags: mission1 doris
---
// Doris the Baker — first encounter outside the Hollow at dusk.
// Per Mission_1_2_Focus/01_DORIS_THE_BAKER.md
// Variables wired through YarnVillageStateBridge:
//   $trust_doris (int 0-100)

<<eyes_look_at "player">>
Doris: Oh — you must be the new Keeper.
Doris: I'd heard. I just didn't expect... so soon.

-> "I'm here to help."
    Doris: That's kind. That's — kind.
    <<adjust_trust "doris" 5>>
    <<jump Doris_M1_OfferOrb>>
-> "I'm not sure I'm ready."
    Doris: None of us ever are, dear. None of us ever are.
    <<jump Doris_M1_OfferOrb>>
-> (silent) Wait.
    Doris: It's all right. We can stand here a moment.
    <<jump Doris_M1_OfferOrb>>

===

title: Doris_M1_OfferOrb
---
Doris: I have something. A memory. Something I've kept too long.
Doris: I wondered if you might — buy it. Take care of it.
<<eyes_look_at "orb">>
Doris: It's the morning I first baked bread on my own. After mother. After.
Doris: It's bright. It's just so bright I sometimes can't go into the kitchen.
Doris: I'd like to look at it less. I'd like it not to ache.

-> "I'll honor it. Five silver."
    <<adjust_trust "doris" 5>>
    <<adjust_coin -5>>
    <<jump Doris_M1_HandsOrb_Honor>>
-> "Ten silver. It looks important."
    <<adjust_trust "doris" 8>>
    <<adjust_coin -10>>
    <<jump Doris_M1_HandsOrb_Generous>>
-> "Three silver — I'm starting out."
    <<adjust_trust "doris" 2>>
    <<adjust_coin -3>>
    <<jump Doris_M1_HandsOrb_Practical>>

===

title: Doris_M1_HandsOrb_Honor
---
Doris: That's fair. That's — fair.
Doris: Polish it gently. The faster you press, the less the orb hears you.
<<jump Doris_M1_PolishHandoff>>

===

title: Doris_M1_HandsOrb_Generous
---
Doris: That's more than fair. Thank you.
Doris: I'll bring you a loaf in the morning. Two loaves. Three.
<<jump Doris_M1_PolishHandoff>>

===

title: Doris_M1_HandsOrb_Practical
---
Doris: Three is — three is fine. I understand.
Doris: Just — please be careful with it.
<<jump Doris_M1_PolishHandoff>>

===

title: Doris_M1_PolishHandoff
---
Doris: Polish in slow circles. Cover all sides. Most memories need ninety seconds.
Doris: There's a note pinned above the workbench. Marin's hand. It still helps.
<<pickle_say "Slower.">>
Doris: And — Pickle. Don't mind her. She judges everyone.
<<dialogue_end>>
<<offer_polish>>

===

title: Doris_M1_AfterPolish_Bright
---
<<eyes_look_at "orb">>
Doris: ... You did it cleaner than I remembered.
Doris: That's — that's how it was. Yes.
<<adjust_trust "doris" 3>>
Doris: Keep it on the shelf. The one by the window if you can.
Doris: Goodnight, Keeper.
<<dialogue_end>>

===

title: Doris_M1_AfterPolish_Acceptable
---
Doris: It's a little less bright than I remembered. That's all right.
Doris: That's all right.
<<adjust_trust "doris" 1>>
Doris: Keep it where you can see it.
<<dialogue_end>>

===

title: Doris_M1_AfterPolish_Dim
---
Doris: It's the morning still. A little dimmer.
Doris: ... I'll come back tomorrow, maybe.
<<dialogue_end>>

===
